<h1>Start a Patient Campaign!</h1>

<h3>Your Patient Campaign is where everything begins at ArtCaring.</h3>

<p>Before you start listing your artworks, you'll set up a Patient Campaign here. Visitors and shoppers on ArtCaring will learn about the person you're helping (your 'patient'), based on the information you provide here.</p>
<p>All artworks that sell on ArtCaring will always be associated with the Patient and Patient Campaign that they were listed under. Please fill in the information below, telling us about the person you want to help through your artwork sales on the site.</p>


<%= form_for @patient_campaign do |f| %>

  <div><%= f.label :campaign_name, "Name your Patient Campaign, i.e. 'Mary's Cancer Fund' or 'Support for Bill's Back Surgery'" %>
    <%= f.text_field :campaign_name %></div>

  <div><%= f.label :patient_first_name, "First Name of Patient" %>
    <%= f.text_field :patient_first_name %></div>

  <div><%= f.label :patient_last_name, "Last Name of Patient" %>
    <%= f.text_field :patient_last_name %></div>

  <div><%= f.label :patient_street_address, "Patient's Street Address" %>
    <%= f.text_field :patient_street_address %></div>

  <div><%= f.label :patient_unit_number, "Patient's Apartment/Unit #" %>
    <%= f.text_field :patient_unit_number %></div>

  <div><%= f.label :patient_city, "Patient's City of Residence" %>
    <%= f.text_field :patient_city %></div>

  <div><%= f.label :patient_state, "Patient's State of Residence" %>
    <%= f.text_field :patient_state %></div>

  <div><%= f.label :patient_zip_code, "Patient's Zip Code" %>
    <%= f.text_field :patient_zip_code %></div>

  <div><%= f.label :patient_phone_number, "Patient's Phone Number" %>
    <%= f.text_field :patient_phone_number %></div>

  <div><%= f.label :artist_relationship_to_patient, "Briefly - your relationship to the Patient (friend, relative, neighbor, etc.) "%>
    <%= f.text_area :artist_relationship_to_patient, rows: 2 %></div>

  <div><%= f.label :patient_diagnosis, "Name the Patient's condition, diagnosis, or illness." %>
    <%= f.text_area :patient_diagnosis, rows: 1 %>

  <div><%= f.label :patient_story, "Tell visitors your Patient's story. (Click here for ideas on how to tell a meaningful story.)" %>
    <%= f.text_area :patient_story, rows: 20%>

  <div><%= image_tag(@patient_campaign.patient_image_1.url) if @patient_campaign.patient_image_1? %>
    <%= f.label :patient_image_1, "Upload a photo of your Patient that will be shown with their story, along with your associated artworks. (For photo help, click here)" %>
      <%= f.file_field :patient_image_1 %>
    <span class="cancel">cancel</span></div>

  <p><%= f.submit "Publish your Patient Campaign" %></p>

<%end%>

